name: OCKSemanticVersion.ParsingError
desc: The errors that can occur while you atttempt to parse a string into a semantic version.

items.name: case invalidMajorVersion
items.desc: A case that indicates the major version is invalid.

items.name: case invalidMinorVersion
items.desc: A case that indicates the minor version is invalid.

items.name: case invalidPatchVersion
items.desc: A case that indicates the patch version is invalid.

items.name: case emptyString
items.desc: A case that indicates string to parse is empty.

items.name: case tooManySeparators
items.desc: A case that indicates the string contains more than two separators.
